import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'

import App from './App'


import { MuiThemeProvider } from '@material-ui/core/styles'
import theme from './theme'

ReactDOM.render(
  <MuiThemeProvider theme={theme}>
    <App />
  </MuiThemeProvider>,
  document.getElementById('root')
)
